{"data":[{"name":"102:1","price":"(1) Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you","arabic":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6169,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"102:2","price":"(2) Until you visit the graveyards.[1980]","arabic":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6170,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1980]- i.e., remain in them temporarily, meaning until the Day of Resurrection.","lang":"en"},{"name":"102:3","price":"(3) No! You are going to know.","arabic":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6171,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"102:4","price":"(4) Then, no! You are going to know.","arabic":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6172,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"102:5","price":"(5) No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty...[1981]","arabic":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6173,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1981]- The conclusion of this verse is estimated to be \"...you would not have been distracted from preparing for the Hereafter.\"","lang":"en"},{"name":"102:6","price":"(6) You will surely see the Hellfire.","arabic":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6174,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"102:7","price":"(7) Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty.[1982]","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6175,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1982]- i.e., with actual eyesight.","lang":"en"},{"name":"102:8","price":"(8) Then you will surely be asked that Day about pleasure.[1983]","arabic":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur"],"ayahNumber":6176,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1983]- i.e., the comforts of worldly life and whether you were grateful to Allāh for His blessings.","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["102 (At-Takathur)","At-Takathur","Surah At-Takathur","Chapter At-Takathur","Takathur","Surah Takathur","Chapter Takathur","At Takathur","Surah At Takathur","Chapter At Takathur","Surah 102","Chapter 102","The Rivalry","التكاثر"]}